{"tid":253173,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"急症室收費增至180元　6月18日實施","createTime":"2017-05-22T07:47:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-23T09:37:31.000Z","uid":11050,"like":10,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c1c9e9e4a7334c8d435e5afc0fb9374b42b1cc7f","tid":253173,"uid":11050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T07:47:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n政府公布，公營醫療服務的收費將於下月18日調整，包括公營醫院急症室服務的收費將由100港元調整至180港元，普通科門診收費則由45港元微調至50港元，以鼓勵病情並非最危急的急症室病人轉往輪候門診服務。<br />\n<br />\n此外，專科門診首次診症費由100港元增至135港元，其後每次診症費由60港元增至80港元。另急症病床住院費用由每日100港元增至120港元，而社康護理服務收費則維持80港元，以鼓勵康復醫院的病人早日出院。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170522/bkn-20170522153345438-0522_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170522%2Fbkn-20170522153345438-0522_00822_001.html&d=WsZpLEGudxUbfaIdpI%2FiYrIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=d134ba44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170522/bkn-20170522153345438-0522_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"3cf896c2abbdb614673bf70fa889ec32b3b13c16","tid":253173,"uid":11050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T07:47:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be9c501b4036a55b14a767cbc366c77f6f6e6ef0","tid":253173,"uid":11050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T07:47:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e232e5e7fb4f78dcb91d81df5ea9e597d2402da","tid":253173,"uid":11050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T07:48:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6472193514478d0c9c47e044b2c94200e8c76da1","tid":253173,"uid":11050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T07:48:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/h